{"tid":566720,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"頭先搭𨋢聽左個笑話","createTime":"2018-02-20T07:51:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T11:32:18.000Z","uid":162270,"like":3,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"48955e3286fa73b5e6bf4d05a10e8ef5fe98ba44","tid":566720,"uid":162270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:51:05.000Z","msg":"話說有一個十歲左右嘅𡃁妹同佢老母老豆之類既人<br />\n𡃁妹：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢老母：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n𡃁妹：我想去韓國讀書，韓國d明星好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/154322_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F154322_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=e8a0d0d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n 佢老母：緊係靚啦，人地整容架<br />\n我：<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係整容都係咁樣衰喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n𡃁妹：緊係唔係啦，子瑜都冇整容架，佢16歲就出道架<br />\n我：<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/20/154945_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F20%2F154945_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b6096f7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢台灣人黎架喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n然後我就出左𨋢喇<br />\n<br />\nbtw，利申：聽右埋"},{"pid":"ed832ab7591d79c4871faf965cfe0e87fc5a7c61","tid":566720,"uid":77569,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T07:53:05.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"425ff367a9dc263e531dbca40d605a04e74b5b31","tid":56